
                 Thot library and Amaya

Thot is a generic system for the development of document centered
applications based on the concept of structured active documents. It can be
used for building interactive system as well as automatic processors.
Currently the programs using the Thot Library and available in source
form are Thot Editor (http://www.inrialpes.fr/opera/Thot) and Amaya (see
http://www.w3.org/Amaya for more information).

For more information about Amaya. see the README.amaya file
and the documentation located in Thot/doc/amaya.

